      "value": "<p>Your companion is a natural talent for the trapbreaker&#8217;s art. The companion adds 1/2 its Hit Dice to Perception checks made to locate traps and to Disable Device checks (minimum +1). The companion can use Disable Device to disarm magic traps. It may take rogue talents in place of feats, if it qualifies for them, using its Hit Dice in place of rogue levels. At 10 Hit Dice, it can select advanced talents as feats.</p>\n",
